With energy costs rising, finding cheaper solutions to keep warm in the house is important to many, and Argos' fan heater is a great option. For those looking to keep winter temperatures at bay, a portable heater is a handy direct heat source.    The general rating of the heater is 4.6 / 5, with some shoppers calling it 'good on energy'. James said: ''This heater is fantastic!! Small, lightweight looks really smart and is so good on energy!'' Stewaje commented: ''Bought this during the recent cold snap to add extra warmth. For the size of it, it gives out a decent amount of heat and will easily heat up a small room. Didn't look too bad in terms of electricity usage. Good price, compact size and good heat.'' Miles also added: ''Warming electric heater that is much cheaper to run than the central heating.''